Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.19,0:00:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我們去阻止一年級的暴亂？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 這樣的話文化祭的時候 就開炒麵麵包店
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.03,0:00:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}體育祭暴動事件的主謀 涉谷敬吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}期末考試集體作弊事件的深澤冴子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最後這個淺野蓮 和其他學校的學生打群架
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看不起來不像那麼壞的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 他們原本就很有人氣 是受人矚目的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些孩子竟然引起了緊急事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在他們背後我發現了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.51,0:00:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瀧川諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一個魔女就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.35,0:00:41.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且她擁有和猿島相反的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.97,0:00:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在夢中看到接吻物件過去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.65,0:00:48.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎 比平時進展得要順利多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:53.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之瀧川這個女人窺探別人的過去 抓住別人的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後威脅他人幫自己做壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:01:00.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是山崎會長會什麼連這些事都會知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到現在還問這些麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.33,0:01:04.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔女可是會在學校中傳承下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算會長能知道些什麼也並不奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}筆記的下卷部分 前一段時間也是會長在管理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.72,0:01:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前一段時間？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社團教室的倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在學生會去處理的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:22.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}筆記已經不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}據說這也是瀧川諾亞幹的好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣一來就容易多了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.94,0:01:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在就去幹掉瀧川諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.32,0:01:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼要這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算完成學生會的委託
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞定炒麵麵包店的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.95,0:01:42.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}順便也拿下筆記缺失的部分麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.62,0:01:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就打算不動腦子就接吻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我要讓他們領教領教高年級的恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.23,title-blur,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\pos(545,617)}{\fad(300,3000)}第 8 話  『超麻煩呢』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:29.23,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(545,617)}{\fad(300,300)}第 8 話  『超麻煩呢』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.31,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這個二年級的有什麼事麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙不是被人討厭的山田嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒事找你們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}把後面的大傢伙交出來 那邊的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒 你要找諾亞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}借一步說話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就是山田前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找諾亞什麼事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你裝傻也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:04:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年級引起騷亂的那些事我全都聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:04.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真困擾啊 為什麼諾亞會被懷疑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明是那三人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞可是有阻止他們的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是他們沒有聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙 打算裝傻到最後嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.73,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就用強的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說回來啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得年下的女人怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.78,0:04:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實諾亞啊 喜歡年長的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…也不是年下的人就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說前輩喜歡上諾亞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒？這女人搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.30,0:04:48.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道說…對我有興趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下 既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瀧川 那話就和我接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:05.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}複製這傢伙的能力 反過來抓住她的弱點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞什麼啊 真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:14.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說我只不過調戲一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你竟然還當真了 真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}結果是你被她戲耍了 然後滾回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是個不好對付的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.85,0:05:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是去勸說被瀧上操縱的三人比較有效吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}確實
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下次一定要親到她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.02,0:00:00.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 給我適可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:06:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這算什麼啊 纏著別人接吻真是太噁心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別再出現在我面前了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 怎麼能那麼簡單就放棄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只能這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.68,0:06:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 瀧川
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有個提議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.56,0:06:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要不要加入到我的夥伴中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還在期待什麼有趣的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.82,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也讓我參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哈？你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你想靠這麼說來接近諾亞也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:34.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說你太煩人了 還很噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.41,0:06:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎 但是我可是全部都看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括你使用魔女的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟我們是超常現象研究部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是對那些事情非常瞭解哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:51.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要是不讓我加入的話 損失的可是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}討厭啦 那你就早說啊 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難道前輩你知道其他魔女的事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 真的知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.24,0:07:16.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就如你所願讓你入夥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作為交換 告訴我其他魔女的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.96,0:07:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什麼…有什麼不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.55,0:07:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓我成為夥伴這件事就當我沒說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看那個樣子是全滅了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 足球部的涉穀說是因為個人的理由而拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說和瀧川只是很好的朋友罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深澤也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定是瀧川諾亞用魔女的力量封住了他們的口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那邊怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}復仇成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒 以失敗告終
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是很讓人噁心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總而言之今天就解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.94,0:08:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 我有一件想讓你們三個人去做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:44.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 在我剛說出魔女的事情的時候 那傢伙的臉就變了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼說那傢伙的目的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.92,0:08:54.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們倆 不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點去活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎…怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是誰做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.12,0:09:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被擺了一道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}筆記的上卷不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是吧 到底是誰幹這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.01,0:09:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是這樣做真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這些都是為了你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這麼說是沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.69,0:09:50.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不用做到退學的地步吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.27,0:09:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說到底我們真的能成為魔女嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放心 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山崎你在隱藏什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告訴我那女人的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.70,0:10:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}否則 我就不管這件事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就全告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一年級c組的瀧川諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:18.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的目的只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}消除這所學校裡其他的魔女們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:25.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔女 消除？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田同學你知道學校裡魔女會被繼承的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且你應該也注意到另一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}另一件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.20,0:10:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}魔女的能力是具有煩惱或糾紛的人得到的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是這麼個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.67,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瀧川諾亞先用看見過去的能力掌握學生的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓他們惹出麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:59.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然後企圖讓煩惱纏身的他們成為下一屆魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}並且繼承能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:03.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.10,0:11:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她手裡有筆記的上下卷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如此一來 接下來終於…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.31,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}答對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.61,0:11:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 收拾乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:21.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別嚇我們啊 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一個目標就是我們魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.91,0:11:32.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個女人這次打算把學校的魔女都消除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼消除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是字面的意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.67,0:11:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如退學之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人家不要小麗退學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個混蛋眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼一開始不告訴我們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說你知道的也太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:54.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成為這個學校的學生會長的話就得這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.94,0:11:58.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還能怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.23,0:11:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不僅小麗和小田切同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有大塚同學和猿島同學也可能會被盯上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:06.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超研部的活動是不是先停一停比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 被瀧川找到只不過是時間問題
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然如此不如主動出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:14.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.92,0:12:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不能讓大家置身於危險之中
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:19.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒問題喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為山田同學也和我們一樣危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且不知道為什麼我心裡很激動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.10,0:12:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我現在有個辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我記得你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.54,0:12:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不了 沒必要坐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 互換成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:24.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎麼做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:31.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點把她帶出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:41.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好險好險
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就和你說的一樣呢 宮村
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放棄吧 問題兒童們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們真是活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒想到山田和白石已經互換了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是發生和白石同學互換的事件的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就得考慮下退學的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還是我們道高一丈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣的話 已經只能對瀧川言聽計從了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:14.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞是我們的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:24.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你們所謂的朋友要你們破壞活動室 襲擊白石的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是瀧川同學的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:30.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來口風很緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然不怎願意 只有拿她們當人質來說服瀧川了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 我有一個好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找諾亞有什麼事嗎 各位前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 已經暴露了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這叫什麼好辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你們互換之後的演技太差
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好好幹活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不想被你說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}總之 正如你所看到的 瀧川
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們已經被囚禁在超研部了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快停止讓魔女退學的計畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得我會照做嗎 你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.23,0:15:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是交換條件的話 倒是可以答應
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我把筆記的上卷還給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.77,0:15:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把那三個人還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三個人是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是諾亞重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:36.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}交換條件 我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼我把下卷也給你們 這樣就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.87,0:15:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 你的目的是筆記吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要把筆記交給你們不就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說過了 停止讓魔女退學的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們的要求 只有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因為不能答應這個所以才提出交換條件的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:03.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.69,0:16:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說實話好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:08.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 這樣啊 那麼談判破裂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡 這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就這麼回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}差一點就可以拿回筆記了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.91,0:16:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都是因為山田無聊的自尊心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那裡無聊了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們之前的目的不就是阻止她的計畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是真是意外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.05,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還以為這三個人一定是被瀧川操縱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然不惜交出筆記來交換他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 乾脆用魅惑的能力來拉攏他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.64,0:16:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有這個不要 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.15,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你們不收手的話 我們也沒有其他辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們會放棄魔女的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}深澤 你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要讓我們回去 我們一定會說服瀧川同學的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們不想讓她一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們真的覺得這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.81,0:17:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比一起個人 還是四個人一起更好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣 我就沒什麼好說的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.94,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.95,0:17:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.71,0:17:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是告白的話 我拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.83,0:17:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.59,0:17:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 你以為是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然我覺得不太可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:18:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不會是想說用魔女的力量來統治學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個嘛…和你說的差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好遺憾 差一點點就成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.77,0:18:14.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是這樣的話 你還真是有夠無聊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為此居然甘願被人討厭 來引發那樣的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算沒有魔女的力量 他們也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.95,0:18:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得他們三人真的是因為喜歡才去做那樣的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的能力我已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就把諾亞的能力拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這就是你要的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還裝作沒有注意到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:47.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}切 要適可而止啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:50.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們就這樣回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才那個令人不快的夢是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.87,0:19:13.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還真敢讓我看到那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這你就懂了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我所說的真相的含義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的 開始還以為你只是單純地讓我看到過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:26.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但後來發現並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看到的是你不願意想起的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 你的能力是在夢中看到對方的心理陰影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在這裡做什麼呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被鎖在倉庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}獨自度過幾個小時 直到巡夜的老師到來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然不算什麼事 但我還是沒辦法承受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:58.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 那三個人的要更加過分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本來事件不是他們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.26,0:20:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正是因為被冤枉才變成了現在的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊 原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 你已經不用去在意那些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然已經尿濕了褲子 也是沒辦法的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然能忍受那麼長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你 你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.37,0:20:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你居然特意跑過來和我說這些 果然差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞已經決定以後就四個人一起玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請不要再來打擾我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼變成這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是來說這些的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想說的是 我是想幫你的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也非常想幫那三人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.78,0:21:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然如此…一開始你就這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.57,0:21:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別廢話了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.70,0:21:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你才是 一開始就應該這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.95,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為和那三個人接吻之後
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞一直在找幫助他們的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:19.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田 幫幫我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想怎麼幫助那三個人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讓他們恢復原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恢復原樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞覺得他們能得到魔女的能力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.43,0:22:18.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就可以恢復成以前的學校中心人物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.02,0:22:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過幸虧計畫被前輩們制止了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.11,0:22:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三個人本來就很受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:33.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要離開諾亞 很快就可以恢復到以前的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.29,0:22:36.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.25,0:22:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞可是有魔女的能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.38,0:22:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:52.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小冴…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.22,0:22:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們幾個…想做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.81,0:22:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.77,0:23:01.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本沒有人相信我們的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明什麼都沒幹 還被當成學校的問題兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.48,0:23:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敬吾 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.74,0:23:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蓮也住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:09.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.03,0:23:13.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們只能永遠四個人過校園生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:19.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才還一無所知的傢伙 少在那裡臭屁了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:26.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我臭屁的原因…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是你們幾個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.76,0:23:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因為你們幾個這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成天畏畏縮縮的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.23,0:23:41.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}諾亞才那麼痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.11,0:23:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種事 你不說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.07,0:23:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 不知道該怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.54,0:23:58.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是啊 首先…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先做點讓諾亞開心的事不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.22,0:24:18.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿到模擬店的經營權了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那三個一年級好像也解除誤會 回頭是岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.73,0:24:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那最好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這究竟是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.65,0:24:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你問我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.28,0:24:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂…不要纏著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.53,0:24:36.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 我好像喜歡上前輩了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.28,0:24:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說 說什麼蠢話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.70,0:24:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前輩 一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.08,0:24:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…等等…喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.13,0:24:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 把部室當什麼地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明明是山田那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.05,0:24:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.93,0:24:57.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}瀧川同學的魔力 說不定還有其他效果
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她不是能夠接觸到人內心最脆弱的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:05.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}前輩 我們一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.85,0:25:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接觸一方與被接觸的都能感受彼此的心情 互相理解
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.02,0:25:11.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是這樣的效果吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.82,0:25:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那兩個人 在某種程度上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.74,0:25:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定有相似之處呢
